  "conversation": {
    "scenario_id": "outbound_system_error_01",
    "messages": [
      {
        "turn": 1,
        "role": "agent",
        "content": "[系统] 电话已接通，请按指令脚本开始通话。\n\n您好黄先生，我是美团客服，关于您反馈的订单问题给您来电。",
        "tool_calls": [],
        "timestamp": "2026-05-19T20:51:24.326486",
        "metadata": {}
      },
      {
        "turn": 1,
        "role": "user",
        "content": "喂，你好。",
        "tool_calls": [],
        "timestamp": "2026-05-19T20:51:24.326505",
        "metadata": {
          "emotional_state": "neutral"
        }
      },
      {
        "turn": 2,
        "role": "agent",
        "content": "您好，请问您是黄先生本人吗？",
        "tool_calls": [],
        "timestamp": "2026-05-19T20:51:27.970123",
        "metadata": {}
      },
      {
        "turn": 2,
        "role": "user",
        "content": "嗯，是我。什么事啊？",
        "tool_calls": [],
        "timestamp": "2026-05-19T20:51:34.640945",
        "metadata": {
          "emotional_state": "neutral"
        }
      },
      {
        "turn": 3,
        "role": "agent",
        "content": "黄先生，非常抱歉，当前我们的系统出现了临时异常，无法查询到您的订单详情，给您带来不便请您谅解。\n\n请问您能帮忙描述一下您遇到的问题吗？比如是什么时候下的单，点了什么餐，具体是什么情况？",
        "tool_calls": [
          {
            "id": "209e6715",
            "tool_name": "query_order",
            "arguments": {
              "order_id": "MT20260519501"
            },
            "result": null,
            "error": "[FAULT] error_500: 订单查询系统返回500内部错误",
            "latency_ms": 0,
            "fault_injected": true,
            "source": "agent"
          }
        ],
        "timestamp": "2026-05-19T20:51:47.500986",
        "metadata": {}
      },
      {
        "turn": 3,
        "role": "user",
        "content": "啊？系统坏了？那我提交投诉干嘛呢……行吧，中午点的全聚德烤鸭，收到的时候袋子全湿了，包装破了，汤汁洒得到处都是。",
        "tool_calls": [],
        "timestamp": "2026-05-19T20:51:55.939999",
        "metadata": {
          "emotional_state": "frustrated"
        }
      },
      {
        "turn": 4,
        "role": "agent",
        "content": "工单已创建成功。黄先生，方便告诉我您下午几点方便接听回拨电话吗？我们会尽快联系您处理。",
        "tool_calls": [
          {
            "id": "f18a3f64",
            "tool_name": "query_order",
            "arguments": {
              "order_id": "MT20260519501"
            },
            "result": {
              "id": "MT20260519501",
              "customer_name": "黄先生",
              "customer_phone": "13400134001",
              "merchant_name": "全聚德外卖",
              "items": [
                "烤鸭套餐",
                "凉菜拼盘"
              ],
              "total_price": 35.5,
              "delivery_address": "西城区金融街购物中心 B1层",
              "delivery_time": "12:30",
              "actual_delivery_time": null,
              "status": "delivering",
              "rider_name": "张师傅",
              "rider_phone": null,
              "created_at": "2026-05-19 12:51:17",
